summary: An ordinance appropriating the sum of Eight Hundred Sixty Dollars ($860.00), or so much thereof as may be necessary, from the "General Fund" of the City of Seattle, for the purpose of paying the award and costs of respondents in the condemnation of a public street or highway over and across a portion of Lot Nine (9), Block Thirty-three (33), H. E. Holmes Addition to the City of Seattle, under Ordinance No. 39798, Cause No. 138673.
